column5: Heres 2 musky me and my brother caught in the last week, his was a pb at 47 inches, mine was 50.5 on the bump board. One caught trolling and his was caught casting
I'd say you had a great week!!!!!!!!Nice fish!
Nice skis for sure! Did you get them deep, or are they still using the weedbeds?

Casting the 47 was suspended off a deep main lake point, the boat was in 50ft of water, and the other hit trolling over about 25ft of water trolling. We where marking bait in the top 10ft of water, so we switched over one line to blades to stay up high and it paid off.
Nice fish Are they both from the same lake. One looks alot darker. Could be the lighting...
really nice fish pal thanks for posting
Right on man!  Good to see a post from you!  Met you up at one of the Callander Bay G2G's a few years back.  Haven't seen a report from you in a while.
